{
  "stem": "2578.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as it was set up, if I remember correctly, since this area that was designated for the ghetto also contained the Gentile population before, the Gentiles had to move out in order to make room for the Jews to come in.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But since it was a small area, more or less, I would say about 12 square kilometers, not that many Gentiles lived in this area to make room for all these hundreds of thousands of Jews that would move in.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the-- when the ghetto was sealed finally, there were about 200,000 Jews living in that area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, in an area of about 12 square kilometers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For instance, our family of six people lived in two rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was considered, in those days, a-- a normal area of living for a family of six.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father's brother and his family, another family of six, came in to live with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So for the-- I would say about two years or so, 12 people lived in these two rooms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It happened that we lived-- what-- it happened that our family lived in an area what-- that was in the ghetto, so that we did not have to move out of it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the family of my uncle came in to live with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a working class people, a-- a-- a-- primarily a working class people area around there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was also a-- a slum area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Part of it, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it just happened that our-- our area was considered more like the rest of the city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was designated as part of the ghetto eventually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is correct.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the ghetto was organized, everybody-- everybody got a card that allowed him to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was forced to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
